text: Bazoches-sur-Vesles is a former commune. It is in the region Hauts-de-France in the Aisne department. This in the north of France. In 2015, 465 people lived there. On 1 January 2022, it was merged into the new commune of Bazoches-et-Saint-Thibaut.Arrêté préfectoral, 30 September 2021 == References == Category:Former communes in Aisne
title: Bazoches-sur-Vesles
